author: schor
msg: [UIMA-2966] add plugin step that deletes m2e maven meta inf out of target/classes/META-INF...  if present.  I tried making this conditional on the existence of the files in a profile test, but maven profile file existence testing cannot refer to maven pom properties, and I needed project.artifactId etc, to form the proper file path. I also tried making the profile conditioned on the existence of a directory, but maven requires this to be a file I think.
